@node not02 "DIGITAL IMAGES UPDATE"

@{B}DIGITAL IMAGES@{UB} UPDATE
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Hello,

We have a few new announcements now...

Some  more  @{B}Space  Station  3000@{UB} screenshots are on the way very soon and we are
hoping  to  finalise the system requirements very soon as well. A demo should be
released very soon... We are hoping for the game to be complete very very soon.

@{B}Amiga  Style@{UB} has been cancelled becuase there are enough @{B}Amiga@{UB} magazines for the
time being and we would like to concentrate on software development.

@{B}Wipeout  2097@{UB} is progressing well and a demo and screenshots will be ready soon.
We  can't  guarantee  a certain release date, but we will do our best to make it
available soon.

We apologise for the @{B}Digital Images@{UB} club for being un-available for a long time.
We  attempting to automate it. When it is ready, we will post the information to
our website and to our mailing lists.

We  have  also  set  up a new mailing list called @{B}Gathering of Amiga Developers@{UB}.
This  list  is  open  to  all  people  who  are/would like to be involved in the
development  of  @{B}Amiga@{UB} software. From here, people can exchange ideas, help each
other  out and get new people to join their teams. To join the list, just send a
blank e-mail to @{I}goad-suscribe@egroups.com @{UI}

We  also  have 2 other mailing lists-an announce only list and a full discussion
list. These can be joined by sending a blank e-mail to:
  * Announce Only List: @{I}digital-images-news-subscribe@egroups.com @{UI}
  * Full Discussion List: @{I}digital-images-scubscribe@egroups.com @{UI}

We  will  keep  you  updated  with  the  @{B}Kijitsu  Warriors@{UB}  and  @{B}Digital  Soccer@{UB}
development. If you join our news list, you will be the first to hear the latest
news!

Any  questions  can  be  e-mailed to @{I}info@digital-images.demon.co.uk @{UI}If there is
something   that   you   feel  should  be  sent  directly  to  me,  then  e-mail
@{I}Stuart@digital-images.demon.co.uk @{UI}

As always, our homepage is available at @{B}www.digital-images.demon.co.uk@{UB}

Best Regards

@{I}Stuart Walker @{UI}

