@node not06 "READ THIS IF YOU WANT QUAKE2 FOR THE AMIGA"

READ THIS IF YOU WANT @{B}QUAKE2@{UB} FOR THE @{B}AMIGA@{UB}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Hello Everyone,

A  licence for @{B}Quake 2@{UB} or @{B}Half Life@{UB} seems as it will cost a lot of money, so how
about getting the game ported to the @{B}Amiga@{UB} by @{B}ID Software@{UB}? It seems a long shot,
but  it  is  well  worth a try. If @{B}ID@{UB} see a possible @{B}Amiga@{UB} market, then they may
take  the  chance  to  release  some  stunning  games  to the @{B}Amiga@{UB}. What I want
everyone  to do is to get everyone they know to write a small message of support
