@node not14 "NETAX1200: A SOLUTION TO NETWORK A1200/A600"

@{B}NETAX1200@{UB}: A SOLUTION TO NETWORK @{B}A1200@{UB}/@{B}A600@{UB}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{B}Netax1200@{UB}  is  the  best  solution  for  @{B}Amiga  1200@{UB}/@{B}600@{UB} owners to network their
computers  in a smart and cheap way. The card plugs in the @{B}PCMCIA@{UB} slot and gives
a fast, powerful and reliable @{B}Ethernet@{UB} connection, in a 100% compatible way with
other  platforms.  The @{B}Netax1200@{UB} is a fast @{B}PCMCIA@{UB} "credit card" who comes with a
detailed  printed  manual, a pass-trough "T" connector for @{B}BNC@{UB} cables and a disk
including the @{B}Netax@{UB} software for @{B}Amiga@{UB} Systems. The software features a standard
system device ( @{I}netax.device @{UI}), that makes the card compatible with almost every
@{B}Amiga@{UB}  networking  software,  including  @{B}Genesis@{UB},  @{B}NetConnect@{UB}, @{B}AmiTCP@{UB}, @{B}Miami@{UB} and
@{B}MiamiDeLuxe@{UB}.  The  device  fully  complies  to  @{B}SANA-II@{UB} specifics, so also other
software like @{B}Envoy@{UB} run flawlessly and with no bottlenecks.

The @{B}Netax1200@{UB} also features a full combo connector for both standard @{B}UTP@{UB} and @{B}BNC@{UB}
cabled  networks, and can also be plugged while your computer is on with no risk
for  the  computer  or the peripherals. By providing a full @{B}Ethernet@{UB} connection,
the  @{B}Netax1200@{UB} can be used to network the @{B}Amiga@{UB} with almost every other computer
as @{B}PC@{UB}s, @{B}MAC@{UB}s, @{B}UNIX@{UB} like systems and so on.

The   card  consumes  no  CPU  time,  leaving  your  processor  free  for  other
applications,  unlike  other  networking devices do, and assures you unthinkable
speeds  also on the plain @{B}68000@{UB} mounted on the @{B}Amiga 600@{UB}. We recommend anyway at
least  a  @{B}68030@{UB} processor to get the best out of your @{B}Netax1200@{UB} and reach higher
speed  rates. Our tests indicate that in FTP mode, the @{B}Netax1200@{UB} provides speeds
